  "detailed_description": "<h1>Upcoming</h1><p></p><br><h1>Update log</h1><p>Version：1.2.385<br>1.0 Windows  32 Bit support<br>2.0 Fix Ui Guide missing bugs<br>3.0 Fix some bugs when you open the bag<br>4.0 Fix“Butcher in tools Room shows wrong QE tips”<br>5.0 Fix aromas bugs<br><br>Version:1.2.360<br><br>1.UI signature in the ED bug fix<br><br>2.UI logic error when butcher in the tools room fix<br><br>Version:1.2.338<br>1.0 sound Ajustment bug fix<br>2.0 Tutorial Added<br>3.0 Bug Fix(Floor hands function Fix / floor 3 )<br>4.0 more clues in 403<br><br>21/3/2019 v1.1<br>1.Difficulty Fix “More easier when butcher chasing you” <br>2.Difficulty Fix “Butcher will not serching small hinding place usually” <br>3. One more easter egg<br>4.Fix Animation “strange door”<br>5.Fix Animation “character special move in 402”</p><br><h1>About this game</h1><p><strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/cd4d96619c4a33ffe229bf0e1e578398.webp?t=1565592533\" width=18 height=18 /></span> Hi there, this is the development team of Hunger Apartment, a 2D horror decryption game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/3bcba7084d3471c15d16f59a0fd83549.webp?t=1565592533\" width=18 height=18 /></span> This is our first issued game, and we choose a different way of telling stories.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/700f2b98bea0304845879e228288cf54.webp?t=1565592533\" width=18 height=18 /></span> We try to create a unique experience without using any words, and let players conceive their own stories.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/700f2b98bea0304845879e228288cf54.webp?t=1565592533\" width=18 height=18 /></span> There could be different and open explanations and understandings for different person.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/1e66cd636619c15ffb5fcd651046f62b.webp?t=1565592533\" width=18 height=18 /></span> The game is still in EA, and we will keep on perfecting it to let it finish its story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/5c4f9480b9bf444dec6c367656f522a6.webp?t=1565592533\" width=18 height=18 /></span> As storytellers, we would like to thank everyone who listens to the story quietly.</strong></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/7fc9c085e09d7a77b3c0ffd50590c508.poster.avif?t=1565592533\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/7fc9c085e09d7a77b3c0ffd50590c508.webm?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/7fc9c085e09d7a77b3c0ffd50590c508.mp4?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>[Please read it Before you buy it!][Game Guide]</strong><br><br><br><div class=\"bb_code\">In the absurd doomsday world, people only seek one dream, that is no longer worrying about your survival...\nHow lucky! You stumbled into an apartment ,which must be the utopia in everyone’s dreams!\n</div><br><strong>This is Hunger Apartment, a place not only feeding you and warming you, but also satisfying even your most insane fantasies.<br>No more hunger, no more displacement</strong><br><br>But don’t worry, the price is quite affordable, just your delicious <strong>humanity</strong> in total.<br><br>However, when you start to find those ugly <strong>conspiracies</strong>，and reveal those despicable <strong>lies</strong>，will this still be your <strong> dream</strong>？ or your <strong>destination</strong>？Will it make you surrender your own<strong>humanity</strong>？<br><br>Will you choose to sort out your minds in a disorder and see the truth in the dark<br>Or continue dreaming in a doze and spend the rest of your life in fake peace?<br><br>Will you choose to stay awake in chaos and struggle in Samsara<br>Or drift along with the lies and abandon yourself in madness?<br><br>We tell you everything in a <strong> wordless</strong>way, will you be able to understand the intricate <strong>Karma</strong>？<br><br><strong> In the world of Hunger Apartment </strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >“Sense”</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/0542da99edef444717835e09bdcf2bd7.poster.avif?t=1565592533\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/0542da99edef444717835e09bdcf2bd7.webm?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/0542da99edef444717835e09bdcf2bd7.mp4?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Two distinct characters<br>Can you tell their different meanings behind?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > \"They \" </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/661c2b470632d1cdcc4edae6c439facd.poster.avif?t=1565592533\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/661c2b470632d1cdcc4edae6c439facd.webm?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/661c2b470632d1cdcc4edae6c439facd.mp4?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Unconcerned eyes everywhere<br>Can you take a breath to catch the truth?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"Conspiracies \"</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/cca0298a3b7723491f5855c68ba02938.poster.avif?t=1565592533\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/cca0298a3b7723491f5855c68ba02938.webm?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/cca0298a3b7723491f5855c68ba02938.mp4?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Behind the silence<br>Will there be a sparkle to lighten the dark?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"Choices\"</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/ec923a02e3a5d35f810c995f944bc4e3.poster.avif?t=1565592533\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/ec923a02e3a5d35f810c995f944bc4e3.webm?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/ec923a02e3a5d35f810c995f944bc4e3.mp4?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Say you won’t give up<br>And hear your as well as my stories.<br><br>------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br>Hush!<br>Walk in, and find your<strong>shelter</strong><br>Live, and find the last <strong>light</strong><br>...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/4584c6f432bc5b43cca93d3909086f16.poster.avif?t=1565592533\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/4584c6f432bc5b43cca93d3909086f16.webm?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/4584c6f432bc5b43cca93d3909086f16.mp4?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
