 Apartment </strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >“Sense”</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/0542da99edef444717835e09bdcf2bd7.poster.avif?t=1565592533\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/0542da99edef444717835e09bdcf2bd7.webm?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/0542da99edef444717835e09bdcf2bd7.mp4?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Two distinct characters<br>Can you tell their different meanings behind?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > \"They \" </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/661c2b470632d1cdcc4edae6c439facd.poster.avif?t=1565592533\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/661c2b470632d1cdcc4edae6c439facd.webm?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/661c2b470632d1cdcc4edae6c439facd.mp4?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Unconcerned eyes everywhere<br>Can you take a breath to catch the truth?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"Conspiracies \"</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/cca0298a3b7723491f5855c68ba02938.poster.avif?t=1565592533\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993990/extras/cca0298a3b7723491f5855c68ba02938.webm?t=1565592533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstat